after each question, =
on a cassete tape and played on a cassette 

player that will be utilized i=
n all three buildings in a known 

haunted location just outside of Phoenix=
, Arizona.



There will be digital recorders, cassette recorders, omni 

d=
irectional microphones, condensor microphones, as well as an 

electrocet b=
oom microphone present in all of the sessions. There 

