nts in the buildings when these sessions take 

place.



My hope is to:


=

Record an authentic EVP with no human agent in the building. 



If this i=
s phenomena driven, will the phenomena communicate by 

responding to quest=
ions from a machine rather than a human agent? 



If you have any ideas to=
 enhance this experiment, please feel free 

to let me know. This experimen=
t will take place on October 27th. 



James














